snippet.title: Hello Kitty Happiness Parade | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Create a grand spectacle with Hello Kitty and friends. Make new allies and lean on your abilities to avoid traps that can rain on your parade!

Play Hello Kitty Happiness Parade, on Netflix: 
https://www.netflix.com/game/81569954

SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/29qBUt7
